[INST] Provide terraform hcl code containing three variables:
    - The first one is named 'variable_1' of type string and value set to 'variable_1_content'.
    - The second one is named 'variable_2' of type bool. Its value must be set to true.
    - The last one should be named 'variable_3' of type bool. Set its value to false. [/INST]
variable "variable_1" {
  type = string
  value = "variable_1_content"
}

variable "variable_2" {
  type = bool
  value = true
}

variable "variable_3" {
  type = bool
  value = false
}